    {
      "id": 1,
      "textArabic": "وَٱلۡعَٰدِيَٰتِ ضَبۡحٗا",
      "textTransliteration": "WaalAAadiyati dabhan",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "By the racers, panting,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "’ By the galloping, panting horses,",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 599,
      "wordCount": 2,
      "letterCount": 11
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "textArabic": "فَٱلۡمُورِيَٰتِ قَدۡحٗا",
      "textTransliteration": "Faalmooriyati qadhan",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "And the producers of sparks [when] striking",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "striking sparks of fire ˹with their hoofs˺,",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 599,
      "wordCount": 2,
      "letterCount": 12
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "textArabic": "فَٱلۡمُغِيرَٰتِ صُبۡحٗا",
      "textTransliteration": "Faalmugheerati subhan",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "And the chargers at dawn,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "launching raids at dawn,",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 599,
      "wordCount": 2,
      "letterCount": 12
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "textArabic": "فَأَثَرۡنَ بِهِۦ نَقۡعٗا",
      "textTransliteration": "Faatharna bihi naqAAan",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "Stirring up thereby [clouds of] dust,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "stirring up ˹clouds of˺ dust,",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 599,
      "wordCount": 3,
      "letterCount": 11
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "textArabic": "فَوَسَطۡنَ بِهِۦ جَمۡعًا",
      "textTransliteration": "Fawasatna bihi jamAAan",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "Arriving thereby in the center collectively,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "and penetrating into the heart of enemy lines!",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 599,
      "wordCount": 3,
      "letterCount": 11
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "textArabic": "إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٞ",
      "textTransliteration": "Inna alinsana lirabbihi lakanoodun",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "Indeed mankind, to his Lord, is ungrateful.",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "Surely humankind is ungrateful to their Lord—",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 4,
      "letterCount": 17
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "textArabic": "وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٞ",
      "textTransliteration": "Wainnahu AAala thalika lashaheedun",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "And indeed, he is to that a witness.",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "and they certainly attest to this—",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 4,
      "letterCount": 15
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "textArabic": "وَإِنَّهُۥ لِحُبِّ ٱلۡخَيۡرِ لَشَدِيدٌ",
      "textTransliteration": "Wainnahu lihubbi alkhayri lashadeedun",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "And indeed he is, in love of wealth, intense.",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "and they are truly extreme in their love of ˹worldly˺ gains.",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 4,
      "letterCount": 17
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "textArabic": "۞ أَفَلَا يَعۡلَمُ إِذَا بُعۡثِرَ مَا فِي ٱلۡقُبُورِ",
      "textTransliteration": "Afala yaAAlamu itha buAAthira ma fee alquboori",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "But does he not know that when the contents of the graves are scattered",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "Do they not know that when the contents of the graves will be spilled out,",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 8,
      "letterCount": 25
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "textArabic": "وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِي ٱلصُّدُورِ",
      "textTransliteration": "Wahussila ma fee alssudoori",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "And that within the breasts is obtained,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "and the secrets of the hearts will be laid bare—",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 4,
      "letterCount": 14
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "textArabic": "إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّخَبِيرُۢ",
      "textTransliteration": "Inna rabbahum bihim yawmaithin lakhabeerun",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "Indeed, their Lord with them, that Day, is [fully] Acquainted.",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "surely their Lord is All-Aware of them on that Day.",
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 600,
      "wordCount": 5,
      "letterCount": 19
    }
  ],
